<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-23 00:53 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5483 &Cx1f; ttd-z
r a BC-OSTLER-COLUMN-SFCHRON     03-23 0944
