attacks this week on an unarmed black man shot dead by the police
are causing bewilderment among members of his own party, who say
they are concerned about Giuliani's temperament and the tenor of
his U.S. Senate campaign against Hillary Rodham Clinton. By
Elisabeth Bumiller.
</P>
