   WITH
</P>
<P>
   ANTIQUESWIDE _ First-person experience of getting something
appraised. (Hutchins, Palm Beach Post). 20.
</P>
<P>
   RAVES-MAIN _ ATLANTA _ The world of PLUR: peace, love, unity and
respect. This is the mantra of people who attend raves, late-night,
loud, semi-underground and sometimes drug-enhanced parties that
draw thousands every night in Atlanta. (Harris, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 75. WITH PHOTOS.
</P>
<P>
   WITH
</P>
<P>
   RAVES-FIRSTPERSON _ ATLANTA _ First-person account of a raves
party. (Harris, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 8.
