   c/o Gweru City Health Department
</P>
<P>
   Box 278
</P>
<P>
   Gwera, Zimbabwe
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  Mashambanzou Care Trust
</P>
<P>
   40 Sandtown Road
</P>
<P>
   Waterfalls, Harare, Zimbabwe
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  Midlands AIDS Service Organization
</P>
<P>
   No. 30 B 7th Street
</P>
<P>
   P.O. Box 880
</P>
<P>
   Gweru, Zimabwe
</P>
<P>
   maso(at)icon.co.zw
</P>
