<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-23 13:01 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5706 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s BC-BKC-RYAN-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      03-23 1127
