<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-23 13:30 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5764 &Cx1f; taf-z
u i BC-POPE-HOLYLAND-ART-(TR     03-23 0855
