<HEADER>
A5823 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r e BC-WAKING-THE-DEAD-REVIE     03-23 0814
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-WAKING-THE-DEAD-REVIEW-LADN </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
EVEN THE DEAD HAVE CHARISMA
</HEADLINE>
  (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
(Eds: Fact box below) 
Our rating: 3 stars 
By EVAN HENERSON 
c.2000 Los Angeles Daily News 
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``Waking the Dead'' is the kind of movie that will one day have
