   FRANCE-TELECOM (Paris) _ France Telecom is buying 28.5 percent
of Mobilcom of Germany for $3.6 billion, giving France Telecom an
entry into Europe's biggest market after a failed attempt last
year. By John Tagliabue.
</P>
<P>
