emotional, and moving scene. Though the 79-year-old pontiff did not
give the apology many here wanted, he said that he was ``deeply
saddened by the crimes Catholics committed against Jews throughout
time.'' Reaction, so far throughout Israel was mixed. Developing.
(Kaplow, Cox News Service). 30.
