r k BC-PUTIN-FUTURE-RUSSIA-N     03-23 2525
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-PUTIN-FUTURE-RUSSIA-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
310-996-0089. 
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
  
 THE LOGIC of VLADIMIR PUTIN  
 &HT;     (This article has already moved to Centerpiece clients. To
