the subcontinent's two most strenuously forward-looking cities,
Bangalore and Hyderabad, are competing furiously for his attention.
Both are vying to become the most important center of India's
booming software industry but he will only visit one of them. Which
will it be?...By Peter Popham, The Independent &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (TIMELY for Clinton's March 20 visit to India!) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (775 words) &QL; 
