Price as tested: $39,675 &QL; 
Horsepower:190 Torque: 199 &QL; 
Wheelbase 104.3 inches; overall length 186.2 &QL; 
Height 58.3 inches; width, 69.3 inches &QL; 
Curb weight: 3,754 pounds &QL; 
Seating: 5/7 passengers &QL; 
 &QL; 
SOURCE: The Manufacturer
</P>
