   _1999. Providence. $22.95. 99 minutes. Closed captioned. PG-13.
Release date: March 28.
</P>
<P>
   THE ARCHITECTURE OF DOOM. Peter Cohen's film explores Nazi taste
in art, architecture and popular culture. 1991. First Run Features.
DVD, $29.95. 119 minutes. No rating. Information: (800) 488-6652.
</P>
