   WASHINGTON
</P>
<P>
   AIDS-FUNDS _ WASHNGTON _ Rep. Tom Coburn, R-Okla., holds a news
conference to release a GAO audit ''describing abuse of federal
AIDS dollars'' by federal AIDS programs. (Turay, Cox News Service).
18.
</P>
