<P>
   TURNER _ The UN Foundation, which distributes Ted Turner's $1
billion gift to the United Nations, announced its sixth round of
grants. While they cover a range of projects from environmenal
protection to empowerment of adolescent girls, the special focus is
on reducing AIDS in southern Africa. (Turner, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution)
</P>
