<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 1ST UPDATE &HT;    UPDATE
 &HT;    The Cox News Service spot news budget for Friday, March 24,
2000.
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   Eds. Adds: INDIA-CLINTON
</P>
