team would have to travel a long distance in the NCAA women's
tournament, and his began his preparation for such a trip during
the regular season. Among the stops for the team included
California, Maine, Texas and Illinois. As the team prepares for
Saturday's West Regional semifinal in Portland, Ore., the Lady
Bulldogs believe their travels during the season, and the team
unity built through the traveling, will help against North
Carolina. (Parker, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 15.
