Clinton listened Thursday to heartfelt stories of women's struggles
for a better life and told them they were proof that democracy
could conquer poverty and inequality, even if that journey was
slow. By Celia W. Dugger. (Scheduled to move by 8:45 p.m. ET in
``i'' news file.)
</P>
