<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-23 20:56 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6271 &Cx1f; tta-z
u i BC-RUSSIA-PUTIN-(TRIMS)-     03-23 0970
