rebounds C BRENDAN HAYWOOD 7-0 264 Jr. Key stats: 13.6 ppg, 72.7
pct. FGs F JASON CAPEL 6-8 224 So. Key stats: 12.7 ppg, 6.7
rebounds F KRIS LANG 6-11 243 So. Key stats: 8.7 ppg, 4.4 rebounds
TENNESSEE VOLUNTEERS
</P>
<P>
   COACH: Jerry Green, 17th season, 289-202. His teams play an
up-tempo style.
</P>
<P>
   KEY STAT: Tennessee has held opponents to 40.3 percent shooting,
31.7 percent on 3-pointers.
</P>
<P>
   SCOUTING REPORT: The Volunteers have lots of talent, but they
are sometimes undisciplined. Tony Harris has been a clutch shooter,
but he sometimes plays out of control. When Tennessee is patient on
offense, it can be hard to stop. Defensively, the Volunteers have
the speed and quickness to play tough man-to-man defense.
</P>
<P>
   WILL WIN IF: Harris can win the point-guard battle with Ed Cota
and if the Volunteers' deep and talented front line can wear down
the thin Tar Heels.
TENNESSEE STARTERS G JON HIGGINS 6-3 190 Fr. Key stats: 6.3 ppg,
