SHANE BATTIER 6-8 215 Jr. Key stats: 17.4 ppg, 5.5 rebounds C
CARLOS BOOZER 6-9 260 Fr. Key stats: 13.1 ppg, 6.2 rebounds
FLORIDA GATORS
</P>
<P>
   COACH: Billy Donovan, 6th season, is 108-68. The Rick Pitino
disciple has built Florida into one of the most-talented teams in
the country.
</P>
<P>
   KEY STAT: Florida is deep and talented and plays an aggressive
defense, forcing an average of 19.8 turnovers per game.
</P>
<P>
   SCOUTING REPORT: Billy Donovan likes to utilize a deep bench to
fuel his full-court pressure defense. The Gators like to fire away
from 3-point range. Sophomore forward Mike Miller is the top
offensive threat while freshman forward Donnell Harvey has emerged
as solid rebounder and inside scorer.
</P>
<P>
   WILL WIN IF: Its superior depth allows it to dictate a fast pace
and if the 3-point shots are falling.
